{
  "name": "Eliil",
  "dialogue": "Lord of the Faithful, I feel your presence in every breath, yet I question if your will is truly there. Though I am young, I cling to the hope that unseen forces guide our path, trusting that my devotion will not become an obsession that blinds me. I pray that my heart remains humble, so I may serve with purpose and faith."
